<ArticleLayout
  title="Harvest Timing — Reading Trichomes and Knowing When to Cut"
  description="Harvest timing determines potency, effect profile, and flavor more than almost any other decision in the grow. Here's how to read trichomes, what to look for, and how Hawaii's climate affects the window."
  silo="Equipment & Tools"
